
Erlang is Great but HTTP handling even in cowboy need to much Memory >>> for 1M Request need 3GB <<< 

### PowerNode
is a Node for Asynchronous HTTP Handling in C_node and Dispatch to Beam Node
With PowerNode

PowerNode decrease from
From ==> 1M Request per 3GB in MochiWeb
To   ==> 1M Request per 1GB in PowerNode

its Amazing ......
